Titan Module Configuration
--------------------------

This is also in the env.sh script in the top-level-directory.

source env.sh

or ...

module swap PrgEnv-pgi PrgEnv-gnu
module load libconfig cudatoolkit
module load gcc/4.6.3
module load cray-netcdf/4.2.1.1
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$CRAY_LD_LIBRARY_PATH:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH
export HDF5_DISABLE_VERSION_CHECK=2


and then ...

make clean
make


Interactive Job Sumbission 
--------------------------

qsub -I -A fus047 -q debug -X -V -l nodes=1,walltime=30:00

NOTE: also source env.sh at runtime


LibConfig Compilation on Titan
------------------------------

module switch xtpe-interlagos xtpe-target-native
./configure --prefix=/ccs/home/dg6/libconfig/libconfig_gnu CC=cc CXX=CC --enable-shared=no
make
make install
